'''Ingrid''' is a friend and bridesmaid of [[Melissa (The Hard Part)|Melissa]].

==History==
When Melissa's new husband [[Brendon]] disappeared on their wedding day, Melissa and Ingrid followed him and his two friends to the practice, where he was being treated for priapism.

==Relationships==
===Friendships===
She was one of [[Melissa (The Hard Part)|Melissa's]] bridesmaids.
